{
    "product": {
        "id": 6572714197028,
        "title": "Arrowhead Canoe T-Shirt",
        "body_html": "<div class=\"block block-layout-builder block-field-blocknodebuilderbody\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<div class=\"clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item\">\n<p data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"419\">Celebrate the legacy of American craftsmanship with this heritage-inspired t-shirt featuring the iconic Arrowhead deck design from the St. Louis Meramec Canoe Company.</p>\n<p data-start=\"421\" data-end=\"757\">Founded in 1922 by Alfred Wickett\u2014formerly of Old Town Canoe Co.\u2014the Meramec Canoe Company produced hand-crafted wooden canoes in Valley Park, Missouri, until 1978. Known for their patented eighteen-inch hardwood Arrowhead deck, finely mortised in for exceptional strength and rigidity, these canoes remain a symbol of timeless quality.</p>\n<p data-start=\"759\" data-end=\"801\">Now, you can wear a piece of that history.</p>\n<p data-start=\"803\" data-end=\"823\"><strong data-start=\"803\" data-end=\"823\">Product Details:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"824\" data-end=\"1027\">\n<li data-start=\"824\" data-end=\"859\">\n<p data-start=\"826\" data-end=\"859\">Regular fit, mid-weight t-shirt</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"860\" data-end=\"913\">\n<p data-start=\"862\" data-end=\"913\">Natural color, 100% premium combed organic cotton</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"914\" data-end=\"972\">\n<p data-start=\"916\" data-end=\"972\">GOTS-certified: Grown without herbicides or pesticides</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"973\" data-end=\"1027\">\n<p data-start=\"975\" data-end=\"1027\">Soft-touch, water-based print \u2014 printed in the USA</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
